1
00:00:00,140 --> 00:00:03,060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

2
00:00:03,060 --> 00:00:04,980
=Episode 21=

3
00:00:09,820 --> 00:00:11,180
Madam Ning,

4
00:00:12,540 --> 00:00:14,019
what brings the Imperial Preceptor here

5
00:00:14,020 --> 00:00:15,260
so late at night?

6
00:00:16,660 --> 00:00:18,619
Tonight, while observing the heavens,

7
00:00:18,620 --> 00:00:20,979
I noticed a gentle glow

8
00:00:20,980 --> 00:00:22,740
circling beside the Ziwei Star.

9
00:00:23,220 --> 00:00:24,619
After careful divination,

10
00:00:24,620 --> 00:00:27,660
I discovered it
was connected to you, Madam.

11
00:00:28,620 --> 00:00:29,620
Me?

12
00:00:30,740 --> 00:00:32,940
Madam Ning,

13
00:00:33,620 --> 00:00:36,460
you were originally fated to have a son.

14
00:00:36,940 --> 00:00:38,859
But your fortune was too shallow,

15
00:00:38,860 --> 00:00:40,420
so the chance slipped away
time and again.

16
00:00:41,460 --> 00:00:43,219
I came tonight

17
00:00:43,220 --> 00:00:45,219
under Heaven's will

18
00:00:45,220 --> 00:00:49,020
to bring you a destined opportunity.

19
00:00:49,020 --> 00:00:51,920
(The ants mentioned an opportunity. And today,
the Imperial Preceptor actually came.)

20
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:53,600
(Could this truly be Heaven's will?)

21
00:01:00,020 --> 00:01:03,380
This is a sacred object
personally refined by me.

22
00:01:03,660 --> 00:01:07,140
Madam need only treat it
as your own child

23
00:01:07,460 --> 00:01:10,580
and feed it rice soup daily with care.

24
00:01:11,100 --> 00:01:12,459
After seven days,

25
00:01:12,460 --> 00:01:14,140
you will surely conceive.

26
00:01:14,940 --> 00:01:16,060
Thank you.

27
00:01:21,460 --> 00:01:22,340
This...

28
00:01:23,060 --> 00:01:24,420
Will it really work?

29
00:01:27,620 --> 00:01:29,740
I have served
in the palace for many years.

30
00:01:29,940 --> 00:01:33,140
What I refine has never failed.

31
00:01:33,900 --> 00:01:38,420
However, this method of gathering fortune
must not be disturbed.

32
00:01:38,820 --> 00:01:43,540
You must stay away
from all bloodshed and conflict,

33
00:01:44,900 --> 00:01:46,059
especially anything

34
00:01:46,060 --> 00:01:48,699
related to military affairs.

35
00:01:48,700 --> 00:01:50,539
If even the slightest trace touches it,

36
00:01:50,540 --> 00:01:53,580
all previous efforts will be wasted.

37
00:01:59,220 --> 00:02:02,220
I used to blame my husband
for refusing to release the grain stores.

38
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:05,100
But now,

39
00:02:05,420 --> 00:02:07,060
it seems I was the one at fault.

40
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:09,720
Thank you for your guidance,
Imperial Preceptor.

41
00:02:10,940 --> 00:02:12,060
Farewell.

42
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:29,060
Thank you, Imperial Preceptor.

43
00:02:34,020 --> 00:02:35,419
I've already

44
00:02:35,420 --> 00:02:37,100
handled your matter.

45
00:02:37,340 --> 00:02:39,340
You must also remember

46
00:02:39,580 --> 00:02:40,940
Consort Shu's

47
00:02:41,020 --> 00:02:42,580
instructions.

48
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:44,740
Yes.

49
00:02:53,260 --> 00:02:54,900
Welcome, please come in.

50
00:02:55,620 --> 00:02:57,220
Take a look at this.

51
00:02:58,140 --> 00:03:00,180
Miss, have a look.

52
00:03:01,620 --> 00:03:02,619
Your Highness,

53
00:03:02,620 --> 00:03:04,100
will this disguise

54
00:03:04,140 --> 00:03:05,420
really work?

55
00:03:05,820 --> 00:03:06,940
Let's give it a try.

56
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:08,619
Father,

57
00:03:08,620 --> 00:03:11,660
don't the three of us
look just like beggars?

58
00:03:14,660 --> 00:03:15,900
Yes.

59
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:17,460
Very much so.

60
00:03:21,020 --> 00:03:23,019
Fresh premium rice just arrived.

61
00:03:23,020 --> 00:03:24,179
Come take a look.

62
00:03:24,180 --> 00:03:26,340
Shopkeeper, we're here to buy rice.

63
00:03:30,020 --> 00:03:31,140
Buying rice?

64
00:03:31,700 --> 00:03:32,820
How much do you want?

65
00:03:33,020 --> 00:03:34,660
We want one hundred shi of premium rice.

66
00:03:43,740 --> 00:03:44,580
Yes,

67
00:03:44,740 --> 00:03:46,019
of course we have it.

68
00:03:46,020 --> 00:03:48,419
But lately, grain prices have gone up.

69
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:49,419
This silver

70
00:03:49,420 --> 00:03:50,459
is only enough for ten shi.

71
00:03:50,460 --> 00:03:51,860
What? But yesterday it was still...

72
00:03:52,540 --> 00:03:53,380
Fine.

73
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:55,060
Ten shi it is.

74
00:03:58,180 --> 00:03:59,860
Why don't you come inside
and have some tea?

75
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:11,539
This is premium rice?

76
00:04:11,540 --> 00:04:13,219
It's clearly moldy old rice.

77
00:04:13,220 --> 00:04:14,980
Isn't this an obvious scam?

78
00:04:16,660 --> 00:04:18,060
Buy it or don't.

79
00:04:18,460 --> 00:04:19,259
That's the price.

80
00:04:19,260 --> 00:04:20,219
That's the rice.

81
00:04:20,220 --> 00:04:22,620
If you don't want it, leave.
Don't ruin my business.

82
00:04:27,820 --> 00:04:28,499
Shopkeeper,

83
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:29,820
I'd like to buy some premium rice.

84
00:04:29,940 --> 00:04:32,020
Oh, Madam has arrived.

85
00:04:33,860 --> 00:04:35,819
Please, come in.
We have plenty of premium rice.

86
00:04:35,820 --> 00:04:37,739
The finest quality.
I'll have it packed for you right away.

87
00:04:37,740 --> 00:04:38,820
Hey,

88
00:04:38,900 --> 00:04:41,619
why is there none when we buy,
but suddenly there is when she comes?

89
00:04:41,620 --> 00:04:42,400
What would you know?

90
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:43,539
(Xing'er, Madam Ning's maid)
My Madam is buying rice

91
00:04:43,540 --> 00:04:45,259
to make rice soup for the young master.

92
00:04:45,260 --> 00:04:46,659
Of course she needs the finest rice.

93
00:04:46,660 --> 00:04:49,540
How could poor people like you
compare to my Madam?

94
00:04:55,500 --> 00:04:56,019
Father,

95
00:04:56,020 --> 00:04:58,459
what that Madam is holding isn't a baby.

96
00:04:58,460 --> 00:04:59,819
It's something harmful.

97
00:04:59,820 --> 00:05:00,819
How dare you!

98
00:05:00,820 --> 00:05:02,840
How dare you curse my Madam!
Are you asking for death?

99
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:04,620
Little Princess,
please don't say such things.

100
00:05:09,300 --> 00:05:10,660
My child!

101
00:05:11,420 --> 00:05:12,980
My child!

102
00:05:15,060 --> 00:05:16,299
- What's happening?
- How cruel!

103
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:17,379
My child!

104
00:05:17,380 --> 00:05:18,500
Let go!

105
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:31,359
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

106
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:35,199
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

107
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:38,719
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

108
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:41,680
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

109
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:46,199
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

110
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:49,960
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

111
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:53,359
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

112
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:57,400
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

113
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:06,679
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

114
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:10,319
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

115
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:14,039
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

116
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:17,679
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

117
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:21,359
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

118
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:23,279
♪Endlessly flowing♪

119
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:29,480
♪Good fortune♪
